featured.text: Then, a local green energy startup company got the idea to turn that waste into energy.

definition.zh_def: 初創公司，通常是新成立的企業，專注於開發創新產品或服務以滿足市場需求。
definition.en_def: A startup is a newly established business, often focused on developing innovative products or services to meet market demands.
definition.example: The tech startup received funding to launch its new app.
